&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#39;book antiqua&#39;, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#39;book antiqua&#39;, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Provide exceptional accounting and operational service to our clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
